results.name: Row 1 of A122289 and A122290. An involution of nonnegative integers.
comment: The signature-permutation of the automorphism which is derived from the automorphism *A057163 with the recursion schema FORK (see A122201), that is, from the first non-recursive automorphism *A069770 with FORK(FORK(*A069770)) or equivalently, with KROF(KROF(*A069770)) (see A122202).
link: Index entries for signature-permutations of Catalan automorphisms
xref: A007595 gives the number of orbits in range [A014137(n-1)..A014138(n-1)] of this permutation.
